---
// CTA Section - "Your Lotus Awaits"
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-bz-black border-t border-bz-gray/20">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <!-- Main CTA -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-bz-cream font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight">
        Your Journey Awaits
      </h2>

      <p class="text-bz-white/70 font-body text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
        Every transformation from Zero to Infinity begins with a single step. Get exclusive insights, cultural wisdom, and ZANTARA Intelligence delivered to your inbox.
      </p>

      <!-- Email Signup -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto mt-8">
        <input
          type="email"
          placeholder="Enter your email"
          class="flex-1 bg-bz-black/30 text-bz-cream px-4 py-3 font-body placeholder-bz-white/50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-bz-red rounded-lg border border-bz-gray/20"
        />
        <button class="bg-bz-red text-white px-6 py-3 font-display font-bold hover:bg-bz-red/90 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg">
          Subscribe
        </button>
      </div>

      <p class="text-bz-white/50 font-body text-sm">Kami menghormati privasi Anda. Unsubscribe kapan saja.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust Indicators -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-16 border-t border-bz-gray/20">
      <p class="text-bz-white/50 font-body text-sm mb-6">ACCOMPANYING INDONESIA JOURNEYS SINCE 2020</p>
